+   fc-layout-breakpoints.js on first render, subscribes with a DotNetObjectReference, and
+   dispatches ViewportTierChangedAction on every reported tier change (including the initial
+   emission). Module-import failure is caught and degrades gracefully at ViewportTier.Desktop.
